('p_082499', 'PHRASE', 'as such', 'na. 本身；名符其实地；见 such 条', 5, 'phrases', '["CET4", "CET6", "TEM4", "TOEFL", "advanced", "beibei", "expert", "momo", "senior"]', '[{"en":"He is our boss, and must be treated as such.","zh":"他是我們的老闆，所以一定要受到這樣的禮待。"},{"en":"He is an excellent fixer, and has always been regarded as such.","zh":"他是一個出色的調停者，並一直被人認為如此。"},{"en":"As such is the case, I am sorry I can''t accept your kind invitation.","zh":"照这样的情况，很抱歉，我不能接受你的盛情邀请。"}]'),
