('p_083328', 'PHRASE', 'in a sense', 'na. 在某种意义上；有一点儿\n 从某种意义上说；就某种意义来说；就某种意义而言', 6, 'phrases', '["CET4", "CET6", "GRE", "IELTS", "TEM4", "TOEFL", "advanced", "beibei", "expert", "gaokao", "kaoyan", "momo", "senior"]', '[{"en":"You''re right in a sense.","zh":"从某种意义来说，你是对的。"},{"en":"In a sense, she is right, too.","zh":"从某种意义上来说，她也是对的。"}]'),
