('p_083754', 'PHRASE', 'over and over', 'na. 转来转去；〔主美〕反反复复', 5, 'phrases', '["NCE", "TOEFL", "advanced", "beibei", "expert", "gaokao", "junior", "kaoyan", "momo", "senior", "zhongkao"]', '[{"en":"He read the letter over and over.","zh":"他把信读了一遍又一遍。"},{"en":"Over and over again, he read the letter she had mailed him, but he still did not understand it.","zh":"他反复读了好几遍她寄来的信，还是没明白她的意思。"},{"en":"Even though he explained to me over and over again the meaning of this poem, I still don''t get it.","zh":"虽然他对我反复解释这首诗的意思，我还是不懂。"}]'),
