('p_084038', 'PHRASE', 'take advantage of', 'na. 乘；利用；欺骗；引诱(女人)\n 占便宜；充分利用；对……加以利用', 6, 'senior_high', '["CET4", "CET6", "GRE", "IELTS", "TOEFL", "advanced", "beibei", "expert", "gaokao", "junior", "kaoyan", "momo", "senior", "zhongkao"]', '[{"en":"Let''s take advantage of the long weekend.","zh":"来好好利用大周末吧。"},{"en":"All you have to do is take advantage of this rare opportunity.","zh":"你所要做的便是好好把握這千載難逢的機會。"},{"en":"When facing this opportunity, you can''t hesitate to take advantage of it.","zh":"面对这个机会不能犹豫，要赶快行动。"}]'),
