('p_084211', 'PHRASE', 'when it comes to', '当涉及某事或做某事时；说道就什么什么而言', 5, 'college_english', '["CET4", "CET6", "TOEFL", "advanced", "beibei", "expert", "gaokao", "junior", "kaoyan", "momo", "senior", "zhongkao"]', '[{"en":"When it comes to sweets, I just can''t control myself.","zh":"一看到甜点，我就无法自拔。"},{"en":"Shanghai has everything under the sun when it comes to food.","zh":"上海这个地方，海内海外什么菜肴都有。"},{"en":"When it comes to love, women are experts and men eternal novices.","zh":"當說到愛情，女人是專家而男人永遠是新手。"}]'),
